{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "67a2eea2c8b73881fdaea193", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 1, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 90, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba2"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "67a2eb5ca6d4514bf2d9760b", "title": "JEE Main 2025 (23 Jan Shift 2)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "The refractive index of the material of a glass prism is $\\sqrt{3}$. The angle of minimum deviation is equal to the angle of the prism. What is the angle of the prism?", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "AxA77", "text": "$60^{\\circ}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "Nay3j", "text": "$58^{\\circ}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "JBcii", "text": "$48^{\\circ}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "XVlMd", "text": "$50^{\\circ}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "$\\mu=\\frac{\\sin \\left(\\frac{A+\\delta_{\\min }}{2}\\right)}{\\sin \\frac{A}{2}}$\n\nGiven $\\delta_{\\min }=\\mathrm{A}$\n$\\begin{aligned}\n& \\sqrt{3}=\\frac{\\sin A}{\\sin \\frac{A}{2}}=\\frac{2 \\sin \\frac{A}{2} \\cos \\frac{A}{2}}{\\sin \\frac{A}{2}} \\\\\n& \\cos \\frac{A}{2}=\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} \\\\\n& A=60^{\\circ}\n\\end{aligned}$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ250123020035", "priority": "Priority B", "isRemoved": false, "updatedAt": "2025-03-13T09:10:05.452Z", "updated_by": "65d0c176a8f74604505ba6f6", "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "61